description: Custom systems made for unshared battles and FFAs.  New planets (2v2, 3v3, 4v4 and 5v5, 12, 16 and 32 players + barren moon maps that work with any number of players) plus a collection of existing 1v1 maps modified for 2v2 unshared.  Symmetrical and balanced.  [ 'NS' in the planet / system names stands for 'non shared' / 'unshared' ]
author: TheEffectTheCause
